title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Oslo Gardermoen Airport - 1.8
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.8 of Oslo Gardermoen Airport. The airport received several updates since the time we looked at it. In this video we will have a look at the latest version which means we will also have a look at the interim updates which the airport received.

If you also want to give this airport a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/25434/oslo-gardermoen-airport-engm

Do you also want to add static 3rd people to the airport? In that case don't forget to download Dave's 3d people library:

https://flightsim.to/file/5452/dave-s-3d-people-library
